snippet.title: The Wizards - Dark Times: Brotherhood - Launch Trailer [PEGI]
snippet.description:
Buy now: http://darktimesgame.com

Featuring the complete critically acclaimed VR spell-casting experience, The Wizards: Dark Times - Brotherhood includes the fully remastered main game as well as the Brotherhood Update: an all-new co-op campaign mode for three friends to explore the magical world of Meliora together. 

The Wizards: Dark Times - Brotherhood is out now for Meta Quest, Steam and Viveport.
